Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 Samekh复活的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后祭典的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Samekh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么巨大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类能拿它怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh并不是坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被我封印着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君回应了我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君已经不属于任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也不属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只须解开皆水封印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh到了零时空间外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君就会成为这颗星球上的王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球是须方君的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你期盼已久的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球上最后的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想利用素体成为世界支配者的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多么无意义 明白了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来你也只是个恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也是你可爱的地方 沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我为什么长久以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执着于这台素体Shinpathy（牙）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台Shinpathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有驯化素体的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 Samekh只能由进藤须方驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我能连同进藤须方和Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他会永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我操纵的Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的一个零件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把须方 还来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我的二刀流师出同门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了结吗 Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh已经是我的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与现在的我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等同于和Samekh战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还未见识Samekh真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些巫女已经察觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚苏醒的Samekh饥饿难忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴求着复活所需的欲望能量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在发颤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的是零时空间的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开零时空间封印的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh为了成为原来的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吸干这颗星球的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那样做的话这颗星球会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Samekh的容量完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类灭亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭人类 得到Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又能怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除皆水封印 进入第五阶段的Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自由操纵时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为它的驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成为时间旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以无数次重复美好的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后的未来会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要夺回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被束缚着吗 时生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急动议！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德的行为违反绮罗星规约第11条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即除籍处分！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群极品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能迎来启程之日的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只是我用来取得Samekh的垫脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么绮罗星 傻不傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人的小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志家的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水的素体？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然从神殿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正中我下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了 Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh在我掌控中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你打坏了它们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所有素体都是Samekh的奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Peshent（口）…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alephist（雄牛）…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是只属于我的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的梦即将开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来我们只是被利用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类染指素体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许对我们来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但素体是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们迟早会面对的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙妮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过这次的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德错误地使用了素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那台Samekh是台错误的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daletos（门）在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的印记？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的印记复苏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yaddock（腕）…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tzadikt（纸莎草）…在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留有一丝辉光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉之鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 未能回归的素体们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑 纸吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团留下的乱摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣脱Samekh的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发起行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢狱的看守者们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此巨大的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么巨大的东西 怎么才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为靠一腔热血能克服所有的这份年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在压倒性的力量面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己跳进Samekh本体放出的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片青色的夜幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明自己的归宿和前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦碎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王之柱…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…要封印Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让Samekh沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说须方君是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为封印Samekh才驾驶的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 地球得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗有它的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅长表演被赋予的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自信一直保护和子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就这么打算的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的儿子和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见其他人看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底看见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你我已经看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 须方还是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事和该做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一刹那 我也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 拓人君这么做是理所当然的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能放任须方那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从遇见你那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是给我们欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那或许才是你的第一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我最近常想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是 没有遇见你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没来到岛上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕那些一心只想着心仪男子的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特别羡慕有了男朋友的琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此深深喜欢上两个男孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做也是徒劳 Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也别说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们今后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会目睹比这更壮丽的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会
